  <div class="header">Online Image Combiner</div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="row">
        <label for="direction">Select Combine Direction</label>
        <select id="direction">
          <option value="horizontal">Horizontal</option>
          <option value="vertical">Vertical</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <label for="image1">Upload First Image</label>
        <input type="file" id="image1" accept="image/*">
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <label for="image2">Upload Second Image</label>
        <input type="file" id="image2" accept="image/*">
      </div>
      <button id="combineBtn" class="btn">Combine</button>
      <div id="result" class="result">Upload two images and select direction to combine.</div>
      <div class="meta">
        Tip: Images will be combined side-by-side (horizontal) or stacked (vertical).
      </div>

      <h4 class="h4-style">About This Tool</h4>
      <p class="justify-p">
        The Online Image Combiner allows you to merge two images either side-by-side or one on top of the other with just one click. This makes it easy to prepare comparison photos, before-and-after visuals, or creative combinations for presentations, social media, or professional documents.
      </p>
      <p class="justify-p">
        The entire combining process happens directly in your browser without uploading your images to any server. This ensures that your files remain private, secure, and accessible only to you. Since the process is handled locally, the tool is fast and efficient, providing instant results regardless of your internet speed.
      </p>
      <p class="justify-p">
        After combining the images, you will see a preview and get a direct download link in JPEG format. The interface is simple to use, offering an intuitive way to combine two images without the need for complex photo-editing software.
      </p>
